{
  "stem": "10698.2",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 7.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I was-- like I said to you, I-- until this day, my son knows-- he's so careful to say things, because I'm a very sensitive person.",
      "word_count": 26
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can-- I can get very depressed about things.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So I-- it started, maybe, during to war.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "So-- and then I took over, like I said, because I was always a nut when it came to cleanliness.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "So I took over with cleaning.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "And even until now, it's not an old lady's thing about keeping clean.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's just with me, when we came to Israel in 1972, the family that was there told my husband, oh, your wife, when she was a young girl, already the maid was not allowed to go through her drawers.",
      "word_count": 39
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 28,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So--",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And then-- in the ghetto-- then they started to close-- made a smaller ghetto.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 29,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "So my mom and I, we went to see if we could get things together and go to the Umshlagplatz, and-- because they promised you, you know, they're going to take you to work.",
      "word_count": 34
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Umshlagplatz was the gathering place in Warsaw to-- to take-- to take the people out.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "They were the-- the cattle wagons that they were taking out.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "In-- on the-- in Warsaw.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "I did not get there.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I'll tell you what happened.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we met a man that was very friendly with us.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And he said, where you going?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I said, well, we are going to get ready and we'll go to the Umshlagplatz.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "At that time, they had the smaller ghetto.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And he said, wait a minute.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Don't go.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "I can arrange something for you to go in to [?",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Schulze's ?] uniform factory, the two of you.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 33,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "We have to bribe-- well, we had jewlry, right?",
      "word_count": 9
    }
  ],
